    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in such incredible shape, it honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s pristine inside and out\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2006 Porsche 911 Carrera S, a superlative example of the 997.1 generation. This vehicle is powered by a mid-mounted 3.8L flat-six M97 engine, producing 355 hp and 295 lb-ft of torque, mated to a crisp 6-speed longitudinal manual transaxle. The mechanical profile is flawless, featuring a factory-spec Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) system and a limited-slip differential for optimal lateral grip. Recent preventative maintenance includes a documented IMS bearing inspection and rear main seal replacement, ensuring drivetrain integrity. The braking suite consists of four-piston aluminum monoblock calipers over cross-drilled, vented rotors, providing exceptional thermal management. Finished in pristine Basalt Black, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior retains its factory-fresh tactile feel with zero bolster wear or plastic degradation. A turn-key acquisition for the collector demanding mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. No accidents. Clean title. Full service history included. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in absolute showroom condition, this vehicle is a collector-grade example that defies its age. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with professional ceramic coating and zero imperfections\u2014no swirls, chips, or dings. Inside, the cabin retains its factory-fresh appearance, featuring supple, uncreased leather and pristine trim throughout. Every mechanical component has been maintained with an open-checkbook policy, fully documented in a comprehensive service history. Always stored in a climate-controlled garage and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents the pinnacle of its model. It is, quite simply, as close to new as you will find on the market today.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in peerless condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment, it retains its original showroom luster both mechanically and aesthetically. Every surface, from the hand-finished interior to the flawless exterior paintwork, adheres to the most rigorous standards of excellence. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a specimen of uncompromising quality.",
