      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty to believe it. It\u2019s been kept in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car from day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that's practically brand new and ready for a new home, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
